    "Another field in which he combined documentation and conservation was that of Coptic icons.": [],
    "In 1986, he was given permission to describe the collection of icons preserved in the Coptic Museum in Old-Cairo.": [],
    "The catalog, co-authored with two of his former students, appeared in 1994.": [],
    "Van Moorsel was convinced that the Coptic Christians, including the monks, should themselves assume the responsibility for their artistic heritage in the monasteries and elsewhere, and should be given the skills and the means to do so.": [
        [
