    "His lectures are said to have been always perfectly prepared and delivered with humor and wit.": [],
    "In order to acquaint the students with objects of religious art, he used to take them on exploratory visits to parish churches.": [],
    "As a priest and active member of various committees in the bishopric of Rotterdam, he devoted much time and energy to the preservation of the artistic and liturgical heritage of churches in The Netherlands.": [],
    "In 1994, he was awarded the important royal distinction of Officier in de Orde van Oranje-Nassau.": [
